BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set json to (do shell script "curl https://api.bitfinex.com/v2/ticker/tBTCUSD")tell application "JSON Helper"	set result to read JSON from json	set price to item 7 of result as numberend tellset price to ((round (price * 10)) / 10)set result_string to "$" & price & ""

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set json to (do shell script "curl https://bittrex.com/api/v1.1/public/getticker?market=btc-pay")tell application "JSON Helper"	set result to read JSON from json	set price to |last| of |result| of result as realend tellset price to ((round (price * 100000)) / 100000)set result_string to "B" & price & ""
